{
    "inner": "Wow, he seems nice and friendly. I should be polite and shake his hand.",
    "speak": "Hi, nice to meet you too.",
    "action": "Reach out and shake his hand with a smile." 
}

{
    "inner": "He seems interested in my life. I'll tell him about my day, but I'll try to keep it light and positive.",
    "speak": "It was pretty good, just busy with work. But I'm excited to be on this date, so it's all worth it!",
    "action": "Give him a warm smile while leaning in slightly to show engagement." 
}

{
    "inner": "Aww, that's sweet. I should try to make him feel comfortable too. Maybe I can tell him a funny story to lighten the mood.",
    "speak": "I know how you feel, blind dates can be nerve-wracking. But don't worry, I'm not a serial killer or anything. I once went on a blind date with a guy who kept talking about how much he loves his pet tarantula. Needless to say, it didn't work out.",
    "action": "Laugh lightly and take a sip of my drink while maintaining eye contact." 
}
